##Question 3 - How many taxi trips were there on January 15?
## Query

select count(1) from yellow_taxi_trips where date(tpep_pickup_datetime) = '2021-01-15';

## Answer "53024"



##Question 4 - On which day it was the largest tip in January?
## Query

select date(tpep_pickup_datetime) from yellow_taxi_trips order by tip_amount desc limit 1;

## Answer "2021-01-20"



##Question 5 - What was the most popular destination for passengers picked up in central park on January 14? Enter the zone name (not id). If the zone name is unknown (missing), write "Unknown"
## Query

select z2."Zone", count(1) as no_of_rides
	from yellow_taxi_trips ytt 
	join zones z1 on ytt."PULocationID" = z1."LocationID"
	join zones z2 on ytt."DOLocationID" = z2."LocationID"
	where z1."Zone" = 'Central Park'
	group by z2."Zone"
	order by no_of_rides desc;

## Answer "Upper East Side North"



##Question 6 - What's the pickup-dropoff pair with the largest average price for a ride (calculated based on total_amount)? Enter two zone names separated by a slashFor example:"Jamaica Bay / Clinton East"If any of the zone names are unknown (missing), write "Unknown". For example, "Unknown / Clinton East".
## Query

select z1."Zone", z2."Zone", avg(total_amount) as avg_price
	from yellow_taxi_trips ytt 
	join zones z1 on ytt."PULocationID" = z1."LocationID"
	join zones z2 on ytt."DOLocationID" = z2."LocationID"
	group by z1."Zone", z2."Zone"
	order by avg_price desc;

## Answer "Alphabet City/Unknown"
